    <body>
      <section eId="sec_741_B">
        <num>741-B</num>
        <heading>Disclosure</heading>
        <subsection eId="sec_741_B__subsec_a">
          <num>(a)</num>
          <content>
            <p>whether it has a contract with any dealer, lessor or any other\nperson or entity for the provision of assistance in effecting a lease or\npurchase transaction;</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="sec_741_B__subsec_b">
          <num>(b)</num>
          <content>
            <p>that the automobile broker business shall be\ncompensated by the dealer, lessor or any other person or entity for any\nassistance in effecting such lease transaction; and</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="sec_741_B__subsec_c">
          <num>(c)</num>
          <content>
            <p>that the amount\nof any such fees, commissions or other valuable consideration the\nautomobile broker business receives, whether from the dealer or the\nbuyer of the automobile, shall be disclosed on the executed lease or\npurchase contract or finance agreement pursuant to section three hundred\ntwo or three hundred thirty-seven of the personal property law.\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
      </section>
